properties.sfomuseum:description: Color postcards issued by Mexicana de Aviación; set of nine illustrated postcards bound together with four white plastic rings.a. Illustration on cover of aircraft in flight, view is of bottom left side of aircraft; “Alas para Mexico” in white lettering at top, yellow border along right and bottom sides.b. Illustration of an aerial view of a city street with multiple cartoonish aircraft flying through, white border around image; dark blue rectangle at bottom, “Cia. Mexicana de Aviación, S.A. Agente de Pan American World Airways” in white lettering at bottom center.c. Illustration of an aerial view of a city street with multiple cartoonish aircraft flying through, white border around image; dark blue rectangle at bottom, “Cia. Mexicana de Aviación, S.A. Agente de Pan American World Airways” in white lettering at bottom center.d. Illustration of statue surrounded by palm trees and cartoon aircraft flying around, white border around image; dark blue rectangle at bottom, “Cia. Mexicana de Aviación, S.A. Agente de Pan American World Airways” in white lettering at bottom center.e. Illustration of an apartment building with aircraft parked on the roof, a Pan Am aircraft in flight at top center, cartoon aircraft to left of apartment building with mariachi band in it, serenading a woman in the top center apartment window; white border around image; dark blue rectangle at bottom, “Cia. Mexicana de Aviación, S.A. Agente de Pan American World Airways” in white lettering at bottom center.f. Illustration of mountain range with multiple skiers and climbers, cartoon aircraft with multiple passengers to left of mountain, Pan Am aircraft in flight at top right side; white border around image; dark blue rectangle at bottom, “Cia. Mexicana de Aviación, S.A. Agente de Pan American World Airways” in white lettering at bottom center.g. Color postcard issued by Mexicana de Aviación; illustration of golden angel on top of tall column (El Ángel or Monumento a la Independencia in Mexico City), multiple cartoonish aircraft flying around column on blue night sky background, white border around image; dark blue rectangle across bottom, “Cia. Mexicana de Aviación, S.A., Agente de Pan American World Airways” in white lettering at bottom center.h. Illustration of bull fighting arena with an ongoing bull flight, a cartoon bull is chasing a matador who is escaping in a cartoon aircraft, Pan Am aircraft in flight at top center; white border around image; dark blue rectangle at bottom, “Cia. Mexicana de Aviación, S.A. Agente de Pan American World Airways” in white lettering at bottom center.i. Illustration of a hanging piñata on a background of a night sky with multiple cartoon aircraft flying in a swoop around the piñata, Pan Am aircraft in flight at top left side; white border around image; dark blue rectangle at bottom, “Cia. Mexicana de Aviación, S.A. Agente de Pan American World Airways” in white lettering at bottom center.
